Virgin Media Selling 650 Million Pounds, $500 Million of Bonds

-- B y   E s t e b a n   D u a r t e
-- 
2011-02-24T11:57:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-24/virgin-media-selling-650-million-pounds-500-million-of-bonds.html
  Virgin Media Inc . is selling about
$1.55 billion of bonds in pounds and dollars, according to a
banker involved in the deal.  The 650 million pounds of 10-year notes will be priced to
yield 200 basis points more than gilts. The $500 million of 10-
year bonds will have a spread of 187.5 basis points over
Tresuries.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Esteban Duarte in Madrid at 
